text: Du Changjie (; born 20 December 1997) is a Chinese footballer who currently plays for Henan Jianye in the Chinese Super League. ==Club career== Du Changjie joined Henan Jianye's U-15 academy in 2010. In April 2014, he made a brief trial with Bundesliga side Eintracht Frankfurt after his impressive performance at Henan Jianye. He was promoted to Henan Jianye's first team squad in the 2015 season.
